      {
        question: "How does the AI content generation work?",
        answer:
          "Our AI learns your brand voice from your existing content and preferences. Simply provide a topic or prompt, and it generates platform-optimized content suggestions. You can edit, customize, and schedule the content—the AI handles the heavy lifting while you maintain creative control.",
      },
      {
        question: "Can I schedule posts in advance?",
        answer:
          "Absolutely. You can schedule posts days, weeks, or even months in advance. Our AI also suggests optimal posting times based on your audience's engagement patterns.",
      },
      {
        question: "What GMB features are included?",
        answer:
          "Our GMB Command Center includes post scheduling, review monitoring and AI-powered response suggestions, Q&A management, insights tracking, and multi-location support. You can manage your entire Google Business presence from one dashboard.",
      },
      {
        question: "Does Adfluens support multiple languages?",
        answer:
          "Yes! Our AI content generation supports 25+ languages. You can create content in different languages and manage international audiences from a single account.",
