      },
      {
        question: "Does Adfluens integrate with other tools?",
        answer:
          "Yes! We integrate with popular tools including Zapier, Google Analytics, Canva, Slack, and more. Enterprise customers can request custom integrations with their existing tech stack.",
      },
    ],
  },
  {
    name: "Support",
    icon: `<path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>`,
    questions: [
      {
        question: "What support options are available?",
        answer:
          "All plans include email support with 24-hour response times. Professional plans and above get priority support with faster response times. Agency and Enterprise customers receive dedicated account managers and phone support.",
